* Multicontainters pod
  * Patterns
    * SIDECAR
      * e.g. log agent
    * ADAPTER
      * e.g. changing format logs 
    * AMBASSADOR
      * e.g. proxy logs to database   
* ```
  ...
  spec:
    - name: simple-webapp
      image: simple-webapp
      ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
    - name: log-agent
      image: log-agent
      ports:8081
        - 
  ```
  
